DATASET ATTRIBUTION:

This software uses the following datasets, which are subject to their own licenses:

1. GLiM (Global Lithological Map Database v1.0)
   - Authors: Jens Hartmann & Nils Moosdorf (2012)
   - Source: PANGAEA Data Publisher
   - DOI: 10.1594/PANGAEA.788537
   - Paper DOI: 10.1029/2012GC004370
   - License: Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported (CC BY 3.0)

2. GLHYMPS (Global Hydrogeology and Porosity Map)
   - Authors: Gleeson, T. et al. (2014)
   - Source: Scholars Portal Dataverse
   - DOI: 10.5683/SP2/DLGXYO
   - Paper DOI: 10.1002/2014GL059856
   - License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)

Note: The datasets themselves are not included in this repository. Users must
download them separately from the original sources and comply with their
respective licenses.
